547
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:45,580
That is Lord Huaiyang.

548
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:46,760
Thank you, my lord.

549
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:57,210
My lord, I've brought you tremendous good news.

550
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:58,650
What good news?

551
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:02,170
