552
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,190
You have achieved military merit,

553
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:06,100
and the Grand Empress Dowager
is greatly pleased.

554
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:08,940
She intends to marry Princess Wuhua to you.

555
00:38:11,630 --> 00:38:14,500
