the Imperial Clan

607
00:42:04,150 --> 00:42:05,980
and the Ministry of Rites
should have no objections.

608
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,810
However, the honorary title still

609
00:42:07,830 --> 00:42:09,210
needs Your Majesty's approval.

610
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:12,610
Huaisang.

611
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:24,770
Huaisang?

612
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:29,810
Your Highness, what is the meaning
behind these two words?

613
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:34,980
Huaisang evokes a sense of nostalgia,
reminiscent of one's homeland.

614
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:40,650
His Majesty is trying to remind that wretch
not to forget their past.

615
00:42:44,510 --> 00:42:45,770
Take everything down.

616
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:47,210
